Empty data file (need to overwrite)

Format data file with 12 columns (no header):
plasma density [cm^-3]
plasma temperature [K]
vr, radial velocity component [km/s]
vtheta, latitudinal velocity component [km/s]
vphi, azimuthal velocity component [km/s]
vt, velocity components tangential to vr [km/s]
i index
j index
k index
theta (i.e. latitude measured from north pole) [deg]
phi (i.e. longitude measured from tail) [deg]
radius [au]
